    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>v0.8.1]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager 1.x]
    Kueue -.->|metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator 0.50+]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies (Job Frameworks)
    Kueue -->|CRD watch<br/>queue management| KubeflowTraining[Kubeflow Training Operator]
    Kueue -->|CRD watch<br/>queue management| CodeFlare[CodeFlare AppWrapper]
    Kueue -->|CRD watch<br/>queue management| Ray[Ray Operator]
    Kueue -->|CRD watch<br/>queue management| JobSet[JobSet]

    %% Integration Points (via K8s API)
    Kueue -->|API calls<br/>HTTPS/6443| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Kueue -->|autoscaling<br/>ProvisioningRequest| AutoscalingAPI[autoscaling.x-k8s.io API]

    %% External Service Integration
    Kueue -->|triggers| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler]
    ClusterAutoscaler -->|provisions nodes| CloudProvider[Cloud Provider API<br/>AWS/GCP/Azure]

    %% Job Framework Details
    KubeflowTraining -->|provides| MPIJob[MPIJob]
    KubeflowTraining -->|provides| PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob]
    KubeflowTraining -->|provides| TFJob[TFJob]
    KubeflowTraining -->|provides| XGBoostJob[XGBoostJob]
    KubeflowTraining -->|provides| MXJob[MXJob]
    KubeflowTraining -->|provides| PaddleJob[PaddleJob]

    Ray -->|provides| RayJob[RayJob]
    Ray -->|provides| RayCluster[RayCluster]

    %% Observability
    PrometheusOp -->|scrapes| Kueue
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI visibility| Kueue
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|job submission| Kueue

